data.description: Beautiful Ranch Style Lake Front home sitting on .78 acres. This home backs up to the beautiful Deerun Lake. Drive up to a covered front porch and enter into a large, spacious floor plan! This home offers both side and rear decks to overlook the natural setting with the lake in view! The entire main level features new carpet and paint throughout. This home offers space for entertaining with its large great room with a beautiful brick fireplace and built ins, vaulted ceiling dining room, eat-in kitchen and ample outdoor spaces. The kitchen features a double oven, cook top and lots of counter space. The basement offers a large rec room space which could be used for many different purposes. This house is equipped with a Vivint home security system including cameras, motion & sound detection, doorbell and phone control accessibility. The neighborhood offers an Optional HOA and membership includes access to swim, tennis and social club. Conveniently located near schools, shopping and restaurants. This location is approx. 30 minutes to Hartsfield Jackson Airport.
